high_descs: walk to the dining table
pick up butter knife from the table
cut a banana with the butter knife
walk to the dining table
place butter knife on the dining table
walk to the dining table
pick up banana from the table
walk with banana to the microwave
place banana inside microwave, pick up banana from the microwave
walk with banana to the dining table
place the banana to the dining table
anns.task_desc: get banana to the dining table

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the dining table
Take a butter knife from the dining table
Cut the banana into pieces which is kept on the table
Hold the butter knife in hand and stand in front of dining table
Put the butter knife on the dining table
Now head towards the cut banana on the dining table
Take a banana piece from the cut banana
Turn back and walk towards the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the banana piece into the oven and close it. After few seconds, open the door and take the banana piece out and again close the oven.
Turn back and walk straight to reach the dining table
Put the banana piece on the dining table just above the butter knife
anns.task_desc: Put the banana piece on the dining table

high_descs: Turn left to reach the dining table.
Pick up the butter knife from the dining table.
Cut the banana on the left into slices with the knife.
Turn to face the dining table.
Put the butter knife on the dining table.
Turn to face the banana on the dining table.
Pick up a slice of banana from the dining table.
Turn around to reach the microwave.
Heat the slice of banana in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around to reach the dining table.
Put the slice of banana on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of banana on the dining table.
